00:52:12,784 --> 00:52:15,971
Yes, I'll get you your firecrackers.

582
00:52:16,294 --> 00:52:19,799
Yes, I'll get that too.
You stay with her, okay?

583
00:52:20,202 --> 00:52:23,899
Promise?
Goodbye, son.

584
00:52:50,590 --> 00:52:53,052
Just a drop more and it'll work.

585
00:53:59,383 --> 00:54:03,602
