how she speaks to me!

618
00:56:18,883 --> 00:56:19,949
Feel sorry for her.

619
00:56:20,119 --> 00:56:24,703
You saw how she was treated
in the street!

620
00:56:25,105 --> 00:56:27,815
She shouldn't be standing
around like that!

