631
00:57:36,448 --> 00:57:39,080
Amir-Ali, come out, enough already!

632
00:57:42,152 --> 00:57:44,942
Don't worry, we were just playing.

633
00:57:46,739 --> 00:57:49,689
Come out, I'm serious now!

634
00:57:56,669 --> 00:57:58,415
Come out.

