636
00:58:04,007 --> 00:58:05,991
Let go of my arm.

637
00:58:08,832 --> 00:58:11,214
Come on, stop whining!

638
00:58:12,979 --> 00:58:15,771
- Put your shoes on.
- Where are we going?

639
00:58:18,125 --> 00:58:21,392
- Where are we going?
- I'll tell you after.

640
00:58:21,553 --> 00:58:23,777
