641
00:58:23,947 --> 00:58:25,852
Put on your shoes and be quiet!

642
00:58:26,020 --> 00:58:27,732
You be quiet, freak!

643
00:58:30,925 --> 00:58:33,193
Put on your shoes!

644
00:58:33,557 --> 00:58:35,463
Calm down, ma'am.

645
00:58:38,024 --> 00:58:39,851
I'm not coming!

646
00:58:40,097 --> 00:58:42,684
Be quiet!

647
00:58:46,838 --> 00:58:48,471
What's going on?

648
00:58:48,991 --> 00:58:52,893
Hello. What's going on?

649
00:59:02,270 --> 00:59:05,652
Pack your things. We're going.

650
00:59:06,339 --> 00:59:10,160
Guess came at a bad time.
Are you going out?

651
00:59:11,563 --> 00:59:14,785
Mojdeh, I've come to apologize.

652
00:59:15,193 --> 00:59:17,256
Just forget about that.

653
00:59:17,425 --> 00:59:19,251
Is Mahsid home?

654
00:59:19,619 --> 00:59:23,202
- Did you want to come over?
