669
01:00:51,383 --> 01:00:53,651
- Is Mojdeh home?
- Who?

670
01:00:53,814 --> 01:00:56,832
- My wife?
- Yes, but they're leaving.

671
01:00:56,965 --> 01:00:59,313
- I'd rather not go up.
- Come on...

672
01:01:01,870 --> 01:01:06,487
Mom says that someone's number
keeps showing up on the phone.

673
01:01:07,294 --> 01:01:09,847
She doesn't know whose it is.

674
01:01:10,844 --> 01:01:13,987
Last night, when was sleeping,

675
01:01:14,154 --> 01:01:17,578
heard a window break,
thought it was a robber.

676
01:01:17,742 --> 01:01:21,044
Saw Dad and Mom fighting.

677
01:01:21,212 --> 01:01:24,718
Dad broke the window
with his hand.

678
01:01:25,000 --> 01:01:28,779
He was bleeding
and went to the hospital.

679
01:01:30,026 --> 01:01:33,894
- He came back late.
- Do you know why they were fighting?

680
01:01:34,413 --> 01:01:40,232
Mom says there's someone else.
That's all she said to me.

681
01:01:40,753 --> 01:01:43,497
Go wash your face.
We'll go to our place.

682
01:01:43,663 --> 01:01:47,204
I'm supposed to see
the fireworks with Dad.

683
01:01:47,453 --> 01:01:49,121
You have to be a good boy.

684
01:01:49,726 --> 01:01:52,597
