I'm sorry, Ahmad. I'm sorry.

704
01:03:00,233 --> 01:03:01,903
Please forgive me.

705
01:03:07,093 --> 01:03:08,886
Go to your room.

706
01:03:09,645 --> 01:03:12,629
I'd like a taxi, please.
For Samii.

707
01:03:13,714 --> 01:03:15,221
We don't want it...

708
01:03:15,388 --> 01:03:18,497
Listen to me, I'm sorry.
