01:04:21,470 --> 01:04:23,613
You defended her at the meeting!

730
01:04:23,782 --> 01:04:26,493
They wanted me to file a report.
refused.

731
01:04:26,653 --> 01:04:29,115
Your voice was on her machine.

732
01:04:29,285 --> 01:04:34,028
Who said that? Just say it
so everything will be out in the open!

733
01:04:34,191 --> 01:04:35,938
You're going out with her!

734
01:04:36,783 --> 01:04:39,607
There's nobody! I'd never make
such a mistake as bringing...

735
01:04:39,775 --> 01:04:43,358
Why did you leave?
We were supposed to talk!

736
01:04:46,793 --> 01:04:49,664
Ask the son of a bitch who called me.

737
01:04:49,825 --> 01:04:54,044
She called to cancel your date!
You think I'm an idiot?

738
01:04:54,529 --> 01:04:56,799
- We're leaving!
- No!

739
01:04:57,680 --> 01:05:00,584
You should be ashamed, Mojdeh!

740
01:05:00,950 --> 01:05:04,694
You put on her chador to spy on me.
How shameful!

741
01:05:04,858 --> 01:05:09,282
- Open, want to leave!
- You disgraced me!

742
01:05:09,604 --> 01:05:11,747
Go to your room, dear.

743
01:05:11,917 --> 01:05:16,613
It's my fault? You didn't have
a date with her between 2 and 5?

744
01:05:16,783 --> 01:05:18,767
Calm down and come here.

745
01:05:19,334 --> 01:05:22,159
Go ask our neighbor
for her answering machine.

746
01:05:23,203 --> 01:05:27,106
Shut up!
All we need is for her to come!

747
01:05:27,589 --> 01:05:32,047
How can prove that you're sick,
that you're imagining this!

748
01:05:32,216 --> 01:05:33,804
My God!

749
01:05:35,248 --> 01:05:36,993
I'm the one who's crazy!

750
01:05:37,680 --> 01:05:41,864
Didn't even know we were
leaving at 4. But she knew!

751
01:05:42,425 --> 01:05:44,139
What do you mean, she knew?

752
01:05:45,616 --> 01:05:47,885
You're asking me?

753
01:05:48,168 --> 01:05:50,913
Swear didn't tell her anything!

754
01:05:51,079 --> 01:05:52,350
Don't get involved!

755
01:05:52,515 --> 01:05:53,582
He's afraid!

756
01:05:53,751 --> 01:05:55,578
I'm the one who got the tickets!

757
01:05:56,024 --> 01:05:59,007
- And I'm the crazy one?
- Nothing is going on between us.

758
01:05:59,175 --> 01:06:02,476
Don't swear, just find some dignity.

759
01:06:03,961 --> 01:06:07,908
You're right, let me go.

760
01:06:08,068 --> 01:06:10,938
Simine gave me the tickets.

761
01:06:11,099 --> 01:06:14,320
She asked me to give them to you.
You were out.

762
01:06:15,087 --> 01:06:16,959
Why did she have our tickets?

763
01:06:17,281 --> 01:06:20,900
Your buzzer is broken.
They were dropped off at her place.

764
01:06:21,070 --> 01:06:24,733
She gave them to me.
put them on the table.

765
01:06:26,054 --> 01:06:28,878
She peeked at them
when she handed them to me.

766
01:06:29,485 --> 01:06:31,310
Calm down, darling.

767
01:06:38,935 --> 01:06:40,729
Why didn't you tell me?

768
01:06:42,963 --> 01:06:47,308
It wasn't my business.
didn't want to bother you.

769
01:06:47,669 --> 01:06:49,858
Put his jacket on.

770
01:08:05,115 --> 01:08:08,985
I'm a terrible person.
can't even look at you.

771
01:08:10,738 --> 01:08:14,199
Had no right to hit you today.

772
01:08:16,841 --> 01:08:20,742
You can't imagine how awful feel.
Forgive me.

773
01:08:26,251 --> 01:08:31,708
Sweetheart...
Please look at me.

774
01:08:40,568 --> 01:08:45,311
Swear on our son's life.

775
01:08:46,032 --> 01:08:50,456
I've never sworn on Amir-Ali's life,
but swear love you.

776
01:08:51,057 --> 01:08:54,006
Love our life,
love you, love our son.

777
01:08:54,368 --> 01:08:56,352
Let's just forget all of this.

778
01:08:56,880 --> 01:08:59,306
We're ready, Dad, let's go.

779
01:09:00,907 --> 01:09:02,780
Why don't you come with us?

780
01:09:04,855 --> 01:09:06,727
No, go. You promised him.

781
01:09:06,889 --> 01:09:11,551
- Come on, Dad!
- We're going.

782
01:09:22,324 --> 01:09:24,466
- Are we going?
- Yes.

783
01:09:24,636 --> 01:09:26,939
Sir, this is yours.

784
01:09:27,108 --> 01:09:30,217
- Come, I'll take you home.
- Thanks, I'll lake the bus.

785
01:09:30,379 --> 01:09:34,802
- You'll be late.
- live really far, sir.

786
01:09:35,484 --> 01:09:38,512
I'll take you to a taxi stand.

787
01:09:38,873 --> 01:09:44,250
- Come see the show with just
- Sorry, I'm running late.

788
01:09:44,416 --> 01:09:46,764
Excuse me, ma'am,
can have my chador back?

789
01:09:46,929 --> 01:09:48,675
I'll pay you back for that.

790
01:09:50,997 --> 01:09:52,665
Goodbye, ma'am.

791
01:10:05,672 --> 01:10:09,892
I'm going to see the fireworks!

792
01:10:12,411 --> 01:10:14,204
Where do you live?

793
01:10:14,365 --> 01:10:17,270
Near the Imam Davoud mausoleum.

794
01:10:17,756 --> 01:10:20,308
Could you wait a little longer?

795
01:10:20,707 --> 01:10:23,577
I'll take you home when we're done.

796
01:10:23,738 --> 01:10:26,370
Can't.
My fiance is waiting for me.

797
01:10:26,529 --> 01:10:30,670
How do you expect to get home?

798
01:10:30,837 --> 01:10:33,945
You'll spend a fortune on a taxi.

799
01:10:34,345 --> 01:10:35,855
Don't want to be a bother.

800
01:10:36,022 --> 01:10:39,446
You won't. It's dangerous at night.

801
01:10:40,886 --> 01:10:46,229
Actually, one of my co-workers
finished late and then disappeared.

802
01:10:47,027 --> 01:10:52,042
They're still looking for her.
People at work think it's the "Bat".

803
01:10:52,292 --> 01:10:54,276
- Who?
- The Bat

804
01:10:54,445 --> 01:10:55,715
But they captured him.

805
01:10:55,882 --> 01:10:59,340
But he's not the only one,
there are more like him.

806
01:10:59,789 --> 01:11:01,014
Amir-Ali, careful!

807
01:11:12,391 --> 01:11:16,170
Could you play with him
for half an hour? I'll be right back.

808
01:11:16,618 --> 01:11:19,726
- Not a half an hour, an hour!
- Okay.

809
01:11:21,803 --> 01:11:25,830
- But, no longer than an hour!
- I'll take you, don't worry.

810
01:11:25,990 --> 01:11:28,577
Just have some errands.

811
01:11:28,742 --> 01:11:31,851
Come here, son.

812
01:11:33,049 --> 01:11:36,996
Listen to whatever she says.
Don't go near any fire or firecrackers.

813
01:11:37,157 --> 01:11:38,666
Not allowed!

814
01:11:40,786 --> 01:11:44,246
Who's Daddy's darling?
Amir-Ali.

815
01:11:44,415 --> 01:11:48,441
Don't go too far, stay in this area.

816
01:12:10,775 --> 01:12:13,202
Give me a box of matches, please.

817
01:12:20,266 --> 01:12:22,491
And a pack of Marlboro.

818
01:12:25,252 --> 01:12:26,921
Since when do you smoke?

819
01:12:27,087 --> 01:12:30,909
Hello, Mr. Samii.
don't smoke.

820
01:12:31,473 --> 01:12:35,093
- What are you afraid of?
- My mom's kind of serious.

821
01:12:36,019 --> 01:12:38,526
Get lost, don't want to see you!

822
01:12:39,649 --> 01:12:41,758
Forget it, who's that loser?

823
01:13:20,606 --> 01:13:22,238
Are you late?

824
01:13:24,912 --> 01:13:27,623
- Can't stay long.
- Why not?

825
01:13:27,783 --> 01:13:29,417
Have things to do.

826
01:13:30,535 --> 01:13:34,357
Thought wouldn't see you
until after the holidays.

827
01:13:35,042 --> 01:13:37,595
- It'll be hard.
- No it won't...

828
01:13:38,670 --> 01:13:42,812
- I'm glad you came.
- What was going on at your place?

829
01:13:44,532 --> 01:13:47,720
- Nothing. It's all okay now.
- You were fighting.

830
01:13:48,082 --> 01:13:50,986
It's over now,
let's not talk about that.

831
01:13:51,352 --> 01:13:53,304
So, why are you in such bad shape?

832
01:14:07,663 --> 01:14:09,614
Keep it as a souvenir.

833
01:14:14,962 --> 01:14:19,307
- So, what's wrong?
- Nothing, said to forget about it.

834
01:14:20,823 --> 01:14:25,519
- What are you doing for the holidays?
- Nothing.

835
01:14:26,288 --> 01:14:28,590
But you try and have a good time.

836
01:14:29,040 --> 01:14:32,464
Take care of yourself,
you don't look good.

837
01:14:33,226 --> 01:14:35,687
Have a good time?
You must be kidding!

838
01:14:35,859 --> 01:14:38,887
Go crazy when don't see you
for one day.

839
01:14:39,048 --> 01:14:43,552
- How can have a good time?
- This isn't what we agreed on.

840
01:14:43,833 --> 01:14:47,260
- Stop, I'm serious.
- I'm serious also.

841
01:14:47,663 --> 01:14:51,884
These situations have nothing
to do with old promises.

842
01:14:52,169 --> 01:14:55,514
Your wife is a wreck.
understand that.

843
01:14:56,795 --> 01:14:59,778
Know. What can do?

844
01:15:00,385 --> 01:15:05,160
Feel so lost.
disgust myself.

845
01:15:05,330 --> 01:15:07,201
This can't go on.

846
01:15:07,403 --> 01:15:12,224
Hit her in the middle of the
street today. In front of everyone.

847
01:15:14,223 --> 01:15:17,094
- Does she suspect something?
- No.

848
01:15:18,291 --> 01:15:21,274
She has no reason to any more.

849
01:15:25,669 --> 01:15:29,365
- Then this is the perfect moment.
- To do what?

850
01:15:32,568 --> 01:15:34,553
For us to stop seeing each other.

851
01:15:36,836 --> 01:15:39,058
Stop seeing each other,
when everything's been arranged?

852
01:15:39,227 --> 01:15:41,099
Arranged?

853
01:15:45,169 --> 01:15:48,516
This can't go on.
It's useless.

854
01:15:48,679 --> 01:15:51,900
Stop talking about that.
Let's go for a drive.

855
01:15:53,944 --> 01:15:55,532
Have things to do.

856
01:15:55,698 --> 01:15:59,237
Then for the few minutes
we have together, let's not talk.

857
01:16:00,085 --> 01:16:03,351
- I've come to tell you that.
- Tell me what?

858
01:16:05,469 --> 01:16:08,179
You're constantly calling me

859
01:16:08,340 --> 01:16:12,401
and now you're telling me
that it's over.

860
01:16:12,727 --> 01:16:15,994
Just like that!
Thank you, Simine.

861
01:16:16,874 --> 01:16:19,143
This can't continue.

862
01:16:19,666 --> 01:16:22,775
But you don't want to understand.

863
01:16:23,055 --> 01:16:27,275
You're ruining your life,
your family.

864
01:16:27,482 --> 01:16:29,592
This is just an affair...

865
01:16:30,992 --> 01:16:35,653
Are you crying?
Let me see, silly.

866
01:16:35,817 --> 01:16:37,927
It's just an allergy.

867
01:16:38,808 --> 01:16:40,635
What happened to your hand?

868
01:16:57,392 --> 01:16:59,061
Are you staying in Teheran?

869
01:17:00,382 --> 01:17:02,017
Forget about it.

870
01:17:02,577 --> 01:17:04,846
We're no longer children.

871
01:17:07,163 --> 01:17:08,908
Don't know what to say.

872
01:17:09,077 --> 01:17:12,616
Your wife would've preferred
seeing you with a whore

873
01:17:12,786 --> 01:17:14,850
than with another woman.

874
01:17:15,178 --> 01:17:19,399
- I'll call you when get there.
- won't pick up the phone.

875
01:17:19,566 --> 01:17:23,024
Why won't you understand? I'll call.

876
01:17:23,314 --> 01:17:25,536
You'll get used to it, honey.

877
01:17:26,026 --> 01:17:29,371
My husband also
was in love with me.

878
01:17:29,854 --> 01:17:33,995
And then one day, he left me.

879
01:17:34,161 --> 01:17:37,065
Please stop...
That's enough.

880
01:17:39,466 --> 01:17:43,130
Think of it as a lovely memory
that is over.

881
01:17:43,294 --> 01:17:45,324
You're going to Dubai.

882
01:17:45,926 --> 01:17:50,271
Maybe even to live there
for a while. You'll get over this.

883
01:17:50,832 --> 01:17:53,180
Forget about me, I'm not worth it.

884
01:17:54,021 --> 01:17:57,481
- Just stay a little longer.
- Don't touch me.

885
01:17:58,049 --> 01:18:00,352
Can't. have to go.

886
01:18:00,522 --> 01:18:03,585
- I'm meeting someone.
- Who?

887
01:18:05,227 --> 01:18:07,860
I'll call you.

888
01:18:09,574 --> 01:18:12,319
Don't get upset if don't answer.

889
01:18:12,925 --> 01:18:14,275
Take care of yourself.

890
01:18:17,152 --> 01:18:18,820
It's over.

891
01:23:14,377 --> 01:23:16,169
Excuse me, sir.

892
01:23:18,643 --> 01:23:22,987
- Are you Simine's neighbor?
- Yes, I'm her neighbor.

893
01:23:23,149 --> 01:23:25,532
Brought our daughter.
She's not here.

894
01:23:25,703 --> 01:23:28,811
How are you?
recognize you.

895
01:23:30,448 --> 01:23:34,227
She sees her before the holidays.
She's been asking to see her for a week!

896
01:23:34,396 --> 01:23:38,741
I'm Samii, her neighbor.
I've just arrived.

897
01:23:38,902 --> 01:23:41,648
- Come in.
- don't want to bother you.

898
01:23:41,814 --> 01:23:43,322
- I'll open the gate.
- No...

899
01:23:43,488 --> 01:23:45,123
You really don't have to.

900
01:23:45,284 --> 01:23:48,109
Thanks a lot. Come in.

901
01:24:04,904 --> 01:24:07,809
My daughter is in the car.
Happy New Year.

902
01:24:07,975 --> 01:24:12,240
- To you and to your family.
- Same to you.

903
01:24:30,867 --> 01:24:32,771
He's sleeping. Can you get out?

904
01:24:45,223 --> 01:24:47,934
Can you carry this, please?

905
01:24:51,922 --> 01:24:54,112
Hurry, before the gate closes.

906
01:24:58,582 --> 01:25:00,171
Put that here.

907
01:25:06,598 --> 01:25:08,311
You don't have to come up.
Wait for me.

908
01:25:08,752 --> 01:25:11,304
I'll put Amir-Ali in bed,
and come back.

909
01:25:11,463 --> 01:25:13,052
Push number 6.

910
01:25:43,767 --> 01:25:45,478
Mom!

911
01:25:56,089 --> 01:25:59,867
Hello, darling.
Be careful not to fall.

912
01:26:02,750 --> 01:26:06,051
- Who gave that to you?
- Dad!

913
01:26:06,219 --> 01:26:08,123
Dad is so nice!

914
01:26:10,127 --> 01:26:11,953
Carry Mom's bag?

915
01:26:13,875 --> 01:26:16,144
- How are you?
- Fine, and you?

916
01:26:17,863 --> 01:26:22,320
You also got
some grass for the holiday!

917
01:26:25,880 --> 01:26:28,783
We'll put a red ribbon on it.

918
01:26:28,950 --> 01:26:30,582
You're still here?

919
01:26:31,542 --> 01:26:35,082
- Can't you say hello, sweetie?
- Hello.

920
01:26:38,002 --> 01:26:40,509
- What is it?
- Nothing.

921
01:27:37,784 --> 01:27:40,052
- Hello.
- Still here?

922
01:27:40,215 --> 01:27:42,768
- Your husband...
- He didn't drop you off?

923
01:27:42,928 --> 01:27:47,034
Morteza,
why didn't you find her a taxi?

924
01:27:47,553 --> 01:27:49,776
He's putting Amir-Ali down,
he's coming.

925
01:27:51,302 --> 01:27:54,251
- Ma'am...
- Yes?

926
01:27:55,250 --> 01:27:57,076
Today, ...

927
01:28:01,152 --> 01:28:03,581
- What, today?
- Quiet, he's sleeping.

928
01:28:03,745 --> 01:28:04,652
Nothing.

929
01:28:04,821 --> 01:28:07,248
Can you take care of the suitcases?

930
01:28:07,413 --> 01:28:09,795
- What did you want to tell me?
- Nothing, ma'am.

931
01:28:09,966 --> 01:28:13,268
If you need help, ask the concierge.

932
01:28:13,675 --> 01:28:15,659
Why'd you come up?
was on my way.

933
01:28:16,746 --> 01:28:18,220
Let's go.

934
01:28:23,167 --> 01:28:24,879
Come home quick.

935
01:29:14,692 --> 01:29:17,641
You would never have been able
to get home alone.

936
01:29:23,823 --> 01:29:28,247
You did a good thing today.
You really helped me out.

937
01:29:29,485 --> 01:29:31,947
Don't understand
why you went upstairs.

938
01:29:32,318 --> 01:29:35,699
- What are you going to tell her?
- Nothing.

939
01:29:36,146 --> 01:29:39,651
You wanted to tell her something
near the door.

940
01:29:42,368 --> 01:29:46,144
- Was it about the tickets?
- No.

941
01:29:46,315 --> 01:29:50,262
You told her Simine gave you
the tickets. Did you lie?

942
01:29:51,381 --> 01:29:54,252
- Yes. - Why?
- Just because.

943
01:29:55,368 --> 01:29:57,195
You don't lie just because.

944
01:29:58,958 --> 01:30:02,577
Mrs. Simine
was very nice to me today.

945
01:30:03,504 --> 01:30:05,012
And?

946
01:30:08,171 --> 01:30:12,469
You shouldn't have come up.
Does she know?

947
01:30:23,403 --> 01:30:27,783
- Drop me off here.
- I'll take you home, it's late.

948
01:30:27,951 --> 01:30:31,094
- Thanks, but I'll get out here.
- Why?

949
01:30:31,301 --> 01:30:34,805
Abdolreza is there.
I'll go by myself.

950
01:30:34,968 --> 01:30:37,238
He must really love you
to wait so long.

951
01:30:37,401 --> 01:30:40,226
- Stop here.
- Okay.

952
01:30:45,895 --> 01:30:47,326
Goodbye.

953
01:30:54,350 --> 01:30:56,699
Can make a U turn up ahead?

954
01:31:17,002 --> 01:31:20,269
- You took long!
- call to tell you was going to be late

955
01:31:20,432 --> 01:31:25,855
The guy couldn't answer me.

956
01:31:28,926 --> 01:31:30,753
Where's your chador?

957
01:31:32,317 --> 01:31:36,299
Let's go.
I'll explain later.

958
01:31:45,436 --> 01:31:48,227
What did you do?
You look even more beautiful.

959
01:31:50,463 --> 01:31:52,050
Went to a beauty salon.

960
01:31:57,480 --> 01:31:59,590
It's at the guy's house
where worked.

961
01:32:01,508 --> 01:32:03,494
Poor guy brought you
all the way here!

962
01:32:07,051 --> 01:32:12,111
- How can thank you?
- Don't mention it.

963
01:32:12,435 --> 01:32:14,659
My wife made me drive her.

964
01:32:14,828 --> 01:32:17,495
Your wife's chador is at our home.

965
01:32:17,660 --> 01:32:20,087
Keep it, it's not a problem.

966
01:32:21,449 --> 01:32:25,554
- Happy New Year.
- Thanks a lot.

967
01:32:41,827 --> 01:32:44,652
It's cold.

968
01:33:22,505 --> 01:33:24,931
- How are you?
- Fine, thank you.

969
01:33:25,216 --> 01:33:28,280
- You really don't want to come up?
- Thank you.

970
01:33:28,447 --> 01:33:31,476
It's cold out, don't be polite.

971
01:33:31,637 --> 01:33:33,621
No, really.

972
01:34:34,407 --> 01:34:36,711
Darling, why are you sleeping here?

973
01:34:37,000 --> 01:34:38,747
Come back to bed.

